name: Umar Ashraf
tweet: Everyone wants a piece of the reward but no one wants a piece of the risk.

name: Umar Ashraf
tweet: 5) if you want to survive as a trader, APPLY RISK MANAGEMENT and protect your capital!  6) the market is always here. Some days you’ll see great opportunities, other days market may be dead. Know when to be aggressive and when to go for a walk.
